                     <interp inst="t17920912-84-defend774" type="age" value="58"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17920912-84-off458" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17920912-84-off458" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920912-84-off458" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t17920912-84-cd459" type="crimeDate">20th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920912-84-off458 t17920912-84-cd459"></join> last, had in his custody a certain draught, signed R. Finman; afterwards to wit, on the 20th of June last, feloniously did make, forge, and counterfeit, and falsely and feloniously did cause, and procure to be made, forged, and counterfeited, and willingly act and assist therein, an indorcement of the said bill, in the name of the said: 
                     <persName id="t17920912-84-person775">
                        John
                         Dean
                     <interp inst="t17920912-84-person775" type="surname" value="Dean"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17920912-84-person775" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17920912-84-person775" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , to whom the said bill was to be paid, purporting to be an assignment of the said bill of Exchange; with intent to defraud the said 
                     
                        <persName id="t17920912-84-victim777" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Dean
                        <interp inst="t17920912-84-victim777" type="surname" value="Dean"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17920912-84-victim777" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17920912-84-victim777" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  ; against the statute
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>A second count, charging it to be with intent to defraud 
               <persName id="t17920912-84-victim778" type="victimName">
                  
                     <persName id="t17920912-84-person779" type="victimName">
                        Rowland 
                        Stephenson
