               <p>I live at No. 9, Castle-street, Long-acre; I am a shoemaker.</p>
               <p>Did the prisoner at the bar at any time and when lodge with you? - He came to me the 17th of July 1790.</p>
               <p>How long did he continue to lodge with you? - Three weeks and one day, he went away on the 8th of August in the same year.</p>
               <p>After he was gone did any letter carriers call to leave any letters there for 
               <persName id="t17920912-84-person820">
                  John
                   Dean
               <interp inst="t17920912-84-person820" type="surname" value="Dean"></interp>
